    <stitle>Side Mount Cooling Package - RE Bus - DESCRIPTION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>The purpose of the cooling system is to circulate the coolant, maintain efficient operating
                temperature, and protect system components. About one-third of the energy produced when diesel fuel
                burns is converted into power by the engine. The remaining energy must be disposed of by the exhaust and
                cooling systems, or the engine components will be damaged by excessive heat and contamination.
            </para>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
    </svcsubsec>
